ed="T" n="0728b11"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0728b11"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042410"><placeName>京兆</placeName><placeName>大慈恩寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A008981">嘉尚</persName>傳<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n790"/></head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0728b12"/><persName key="A008981">釋嘉尚</persName>，未知何許人也。慧性天資，瓌奇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g581"/>氣<lb
ed="T" n="0728b13"/>質，篇聚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g582"/>堅守，性相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g583"/>克<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g560"/>攻，勤在進修，務於翻<lb
ed="T" n="0728b14"/>譯。遠棲心于<persName key="A000294">奘<roleName>三藏</roleName></persName>門，見宗廟之富，窺室<lb
ed="T" n="0728b15"/>家之好<ptr target="#n584"/>。久稽考《瑜伽師地》<ptr target="#n1511"/>、《佛地論旨》<ptr target="#n63"/>、《成唯<lb
ed="T" n="0728b16"/>識論》<ptr target="#n767"/>，深得義趣。隨<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000042745">玉華宮</placeName>譯《大般若<lb
ed="T" n="0728b17"/>經》<ptr target="#n792"/>，充證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>綴文<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g224"/>，多能傑出。及<ref type="person" target="#A000294">三藏</ref>有疾，<lb
ed="T" n="0728b18"/>命<persName key="A008981">尚</persName>具錄所翻經論合七十五部，總一千三<lb
ed="T" n="0728b19"/>百三十五卷。又錄<persName key="A004093">俱胝</persName>畫像一千幀，造十<lb
ed="T" n="0728b20"/><persName key="A004093">俱胝</persName>像，寫經、放生、<anchor xml:id="beg0728sgsz4"/>然<anchor xml:id="end0728sgsz4"/>燈，令<persName key="A008981">尚</persName>宣讀<ptr target="#n585"/>。<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>合掌<lb
ed="T" n="0728b21"/>歡喜曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A000294">吾</ref>心中願也，<ref type="person" target="#A008981">汝</ref>代導之，得沒而無<lb
ed="T" n="0728b22"/>悔焉。」<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>卒，著述疏鈔出雜集，義門<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g586"/>夥多。<lb
ed="T" n="0728b23"/><date from-iso="+0684-10-22" key="j19711811978588" to-iso="+0705-02-02">天后朝</date>同<persName key="A008985">薄塵</persName>、<persName key="A008979">靈辯</persName>等預譯場證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>，功績<lb
ed="T" n="0728b24"/>愈繁<ptr target="#n587"/>。<persName key="A008981">尚</persName>初侍<persName key="A000294">奘<roleName>師</roleName></persName>在<placeName key="PL000000042745">玉華宮</placeName>翻經，至初<lb
ed="T" n="0728b25"/>會《嚴淨佛土品》<ptr target="#n588"/>，說諸佛菩薩以神通願力，盛<lb
ed="T" n="0728b26"/>大千界上妙珍寶、諸妙香花及意樂所生五<lb
ed="T" n="0728b27"/>塵妙境供養莊嚴說法處，與寺主<persName key="A009213">慧德</persName>夜<lb
ed="T" n="0728b28"/>覩<placeName key="PL000000042745">玉華寺</placeName>內廣博嚴淨，伎樂盈滿。又聞三堂<lb
ed="T" n="0728b29"/>講法。明日白<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>，歡喜符合。<persName key="A008981">尚</persName>不知所終<ptr target="#n793"/>。</p>
